the American Coal Company New Era Mine take 5 spots. Lets take a look at its second quarter of 2005:

##        ai_dt days_lost          ai_class_desc
## 1 2005-05-20       332   FALL OF ROOF OR BACK
## 2 2005-04-16       321  HANDLING OF MATERIALS
## 3 2005-05-05       303   FALL OF ROOF OR BACK
## 4 2005-06-29       287 SLIP OR FALL OF PERSON
## 5 2005-05-04       218   FALL OF ROOF OR BACK
## 6 2005-04-23       201 SLIP OR FALL OF PERSON

In particular, the top accident was:

## [1] "Employee was at the miner when the top started working. A rock fell from the roof, striking him on the leg."

and the second to top accident was:

## [1] "EMPLOYEE REACHED ABOVE HIS HEAD TO PUSH A 2 INCH WATER LINE BACK IN PLACE WHEN HE FELT A SHARP PAIN IN HIS LEFT LEG AND BACK. LOST TIME INJURY AS OF 04.22.05"
